# Next.js conventions (TECNOX)

- Use **`next/link`** with **`href`**, not TanStack `Link` / `to`.
- Prefer **`next/image`** for photos; product images may use `string | StaticImageData` from `@/lib/products` — use **`staticSrc()`** from `@/lib/static-asset`** when a plain `<img src>` needs a string.
- Mark interactive / hook-using components with **`"use client"`** at the top.
- Cart persistence key: **`tecnox.cart.v1`** (see `CartContext`).
- Product URLs: **`/produkter/[slug]`** — no nested `$slug` route params.
